name: ⛰ 🌈 🌳 #unattainablelandscapes
description: ⛰ 🌈 🌳 #unattainablelandscapes is part of the Unattainable Landscapes series by Niki Selken. Because of the confinement I've experience due to COVID, I started creating landscapes I could not see while staying at home. Dreamscapes or unattainable landscapes that combine photos of far off places and layered with impossible weather patterns, waving rainbows, and even shimmering hair.
